Porta di Jaci, now Piazza Stesicoro<geo>37.507408, 15.085606</geo>.</provenance>\n                        <provenance type=\"observed\">Display, Voci di pietra no.19</provenance>\n                        <provenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\" resp=\"#JP\">2017.03.20</provenance>\n                        <acquisition/>\n                    </history>\n                    \n                </msDesc>\n            </sourceDesc>\n        </fileDesc>\n        <encodingDesc>\n             <p>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines</p>\n             <xi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                 <xi:fallback>\n                     <p>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values</p>\n                 </xi:fallback>\n             </xi:include>\n\t  <xi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n\t     <xi:fallback>\n\t       <p>ISicily glyphs authority list</p>\n\t     </xi:fallback>\n\t   </xi:include>\n         </encodingDesc>\n        <profileDesc>\n            <calendarDesc>\n                <calendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    <p>Julian Calendar</p>\n                </calendar>\n            </calendarDesc>\n            <langUsage>\n                <language ident=\"en\">English</language>\n                <language ident=\"it\">Italian</language>\n                <language ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek</language>\n                <language ident=\"la\">Latin</language>\n                <language ident=\"he\">Hebrew</language>\n                <language ident=\"phn\">Phoenician</language>\n                <language ident=\"xpu\">Punic</language>\n                <language ident=\"osc\">Oscan</language>\n                <language ident=\"xly\">Elymian</language>\n                <language ident=\"scx\">Sikel</language>\n                <language ident=\"sxc\">Sikan</language>\n            </langUsage>\n            <textClass>\n                <keywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    <term ana=\"#function.funerary\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html\">funerary</term>\n                </keywords>\n            </textClass>\n        </profileDesc>\n        <revisionDesc status=\"edited\">\n            <listChange>\n                <change when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database</change>\n                <change when=\"2017-06-11\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag made initial revisions to the EpiDoc and added\n                    translation\n                </change>\n                <change when=\"2017-07-06\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag added elements for parallel Italian</change>\n                <change when=\"2017-07-11\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag added additional metadata and edited the text</change>\n                <change when=\"2020-09-10\" who=\"#system\">Updated Zenodo DOI</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers</change>\n\t\t<change when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography</change>\n\t    <change when=\"2020-12-17\" who=\"#system\">Updated Zenodo DOI</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references</change>\n\t</listChange>\n        </revisionDesc>\n    </teiHeader>\n    <facsimile>\n        <surface type=\"front\">\n            <graphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000340_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                <desc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana</desc>\n            </graphic>\n            <graphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000340.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                <desc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana</desc>\n            </graphic>\n         </surface>\n    </facsimile>\n    <text>\n        <body>\n            <div type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                <ab>\n                    <lb n=\"1\"/>\n                    <expan>\n                        <abbr>D</abbr>\n                        <ex>is</ex>\n                    </expan>\n                    ·\n                    <expan>\n                        <abbr>M</abbr>\n                        <ex>anibus</ex>\n                    </expan>\n                    ·\n                    <expan>\n                        <abbr>s</abbr>\n                        <ex>acrum</ex>\n                    </expan>\n                    ·\n                    <lb n=\"2\"/>\n                    <expan>\n                        <abbr>L</abbr>\n                        <ex>ucius</ex>\n                    </expan>\n                    ·\n                    Cassius\n                    <lb n=\"3\"/>\n                    Hermes ·\n                    <lb n=\"4\"/>\n                    optimus ·\n                    <lb n=\"5\"/>\n                    virorum ·\n                    <lb n=\"6\"/>\n                    <expan>\n                        <abbr>vix</abbr>\n                        <ex>it</ex>\n                    </expan>\n                    ·\n                    <expan>\n                        <abbr>ann</abbr>\n                        <ex>is</ex>\n                    </expan>\n                    ·\n                    <num value=\"60\">LX</num>\n                    <lb n=\"7\"/>\n                    <num value=\"4\">IIII</num>\n                    ·\n                    <expan>\n                        <abbr>f</abbr>\n                        <ex>ilii</ex>\n                    </expan>\n                    ·\n                    <expan>\n                        <abbr>p</abbr>\n                        <ex>osuerunt</ex>\n                    </expan>\n                    ·\n                    <expan>\n                        <abbr>p</abbr>\n                        <ex>atri</ex>\n                    </expan>\n                    ·\n                    <expan>\n                        <abbr>m</abbr>\n                        <ex>erenti</ex>\n                    </expan>\n                    ·\n                </ab>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"apparatus\">\n                <p><!--external apparatus criticus (if applicable)--></p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                <p>Sacred to the spirits of the underworld. Lucius Cassius Hermes, best of men, lived for 60 years. His\n                    four children set this up for a deserving father.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#SA\">\n                <p>Consacrato agli Dei Mani, Lucio Cassio Hermes, ottimo tra gli uomini, visse 60 anni. I quattro figli\n                    posero per il padre meritevole.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"commentary\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n                <p>The deceased is a Roman citizen. The Greek cognomen, ‘Hermes’ suggests that he or one of his\n                    ancestors was either a Greek Sicilian or a freed slave. The phrase optimus virorum is unusual and so\n                    is the last line: abbreviations are very common in Latin epigraphy, but they are not always easy to\n                    resolve - epigraphers solve them by comparing with other texts, but this does not have an exact\n                    parallel.</p>\n                <p>This inscription was found in or near the same tomb as ISic000378. The style of the inscriptions is\n                    similar, but the form of the letters is not identical, and the texts were engraved by different\n                    people. They could be approximately contemporary. It is impossible to know if Tyche and Hermes were\n                    related.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"bibliography\">\n                <listBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        <citedRange>\n                            <ref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650759\">10.7056</ref>\n                        </citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                        <citedRange>66</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl/>\n                </listBibl>\n\t   <listBibl type=\"discussion\"><bibl/></listBibl>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>\n",
